                            <comment id="13086104" author="jfarrell" created="Wed, 17 Aug 2011 03:31:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thoughts on moving the client from ${prefix}/include/thrift to ${prefix}/include/thrift/client/g_libc to avoid collisions on thrift.h ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13104275" author="jfarrell" created="Wed, 14 Sep 2011 05:55:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;My first patch had a typo, updated header install location to ${prefix}/include/thrift/client/c_glib&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13220630" author="jfarrell" created="Fri, 2 Mar 2012 02:51:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Moved c_glib headers to $(includedir)/thrift/c_glib to avoid collisions with cpp headers&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13220652" author="hudson" created="Fri, 2 Mar 2012 03:47:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Thrift #421 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/Thrift/421/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/Thrift/421/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-1128&quot; title=&quot;MAC OS X: thrift.h incompatibility with Thrift.h&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;THRIFT-1128&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;THRIFT-1128&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;:MAC OS X thrift.h incompatibility with Thrift.h&lt;br/&gt;
Client: cpp, c_glib&lt;br/&gt;
Patch: Jake Farrell&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Moving c_glib headers into $(includedir)/thrift/c_glib to not collide with cpp headers. (Revision 1296038)&lt;/p&gt;

